function FindProxyForURL(url, host) {
  return "PROXY proxy.example.com:8080";
}
.PAC files are often used to implement complex proxy configurations that depend on the type of request, the destination of the request, or the location of the client. They can also be used to bypass certain types of web content filters or to enforce compliance with internet usage policies.
